WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Every one of these shorts ends the same way. Win big. So here's what it actually means.

00:06.000 --> 00:15.000
It's not curing diabetes. It's not being perfect. It's not one big day. It's smaller than that.

00:15.000 --> 00:23.000
It's winning today. One small choice at a time.

00:23.000 --> 00:34.000
You already know the wins. Know your numbers. Look at your feet. Eat to win. Move a little. Own your data. And ask for help.

00:34.000 --> 00:42.000
Small wins stack. Day after day, they become a life your body can trust.

00:42.000 --> 00:49.000
So win for yourself. Win for your family. That's the daily grind — follow the wins.

00:49.000 --> 00:57.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:57.000 --> 01:04.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
